{"tid":2068934,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ插沙 午市自助餐","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T06:51:25.000Z","uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8ab6c2ce587210d8aa8970ae17114f00cc243d","tid":2068934,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"嚟緊父親節<br />\n想請屋企人去酒店食餐buffet<br />\n因為家父夜晚要工作同埋星期日唔得閒<br />\n所以想喺星期六中午食<br />\n其實以前過時過節都會去酒店食自助餐<br />\n但試過好多間都伏伏地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚普遍就好啲<br />\n有冇連登巴絲有好介紹<br />\n筆值500-600左右一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係好推薦 貴少少都得<br />\n最好係九龍同埋有得泊車<br />\n唔該晒各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ff01b77123d909bcf3bcdd4197868d2b679ead","tid":2068934,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"continental"},{"pid":"d77715e7c85d88b67cb8dc268749506ba96e4f1a","tid":2068934,"uid":15882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"Eaton普慶餐廳，高質黃店"},{"pid":"83ed1a598ba181d432242348c4ad429375f4764b","tid":2068934,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ff01b77123d909bcf3bcdd4197868d2b679ead","tid":2068934,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"continental"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"上網search已結業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6f9fdbd40b77d00d16424f275fd0fa41236d8c","tid":2068934,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0